description: Galantas Gold Corporation engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of gold properties primarily in Omagh, Northern Ireland. The company owns and operates a producing open-pit gold mine near Omagh, which covers an area of 189 square kilometers. It also produces by-products of silver and lead. The company was formerly known as European Gold Resources Inc. and changed its name to Galantas Gold Corporation in May 2004. Galantas Gold Corporation was founded in 1996 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Mario  Stifano C.A., CPA, CA
